rows.label: qst400108_msg0001
rows.name:
Rex, you're back, mo? Did
you forget something, mo?

rows.label: qst400108_msg0002
rows.name:
Nope, didn't forget anything.
I just wanted to ask about
another money transfer.

rows.label: qst400108_msg0003
rows.name:
Find some loose change, mo? The
Nopon around here are all cheapskates,
so you should return it, mo.

rows.label: qst400108_msg0004
rows.name:
It's not that. I came
into a lot of money.

rows.label: qst400108_msg0005
rows.name: A lot... Like, 2000G, mo?

rows.label: qst400108_msg0006
rows.name: I'd rather not say it too loud, but...

rows.label: qst400108_msg0007
rows.name: It's about 100,000G.

rows.label: qst400108_msg0008
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]A HUNDRED THOUSAND, MO?!!

rows.label: qst400108_msg0009
rows.name: [ML:Feeling ]I said not so loud...!

rows.label: qst400108_msg0010
rows.name: Oh, my apologies, mo!

rows.label: qst400108_msg0011
rows.name: But how did you...

rows.label: qst400108_msg0012
rows.name:
No, no, don't tell me,
mo! I don't want to get
mixed up in trouble, mo!

rows.label: qst400108_msg0013
rows.name: I don't think it's that big a deal...

rows.label: qst400108_msg0014
rows.name:
Rex... I can't accept that
much money here, mo. It's
safer to use a courier, mo.

rows.label: qst400108_msg0015
rows.name:
I always give the money I
receive to the courier,
Maxim-san, anyway, mo.

rows.label: qst400108_msg0016
rows.name: Oh, I see! Maxim-san, I know him.

rows.label: qst400108_msg0017
rows.name:
So he was the one delivering the
money for me all this time...

rows.label: qst400108_msg0018
rows.name:
That makes things easier, mo! Do
you know where to find him, mo?

rows.label: qst400108_msg0019
rows.name:
Yeah, I'm good. He's just
past the Avaritia Bazaar,
right? Thanks, Meroro-san.

rows.label: qst400108_msg0101
rows.name:
You still don't know where
to find Maxim-san, mo?

rows.label: qst400108_msg0102
rows.name:
Don't go up the stairs to the
Chairman's room. Take the small
staircase on the right down, mo.

rows.label: qst400108_msg0103
rows.name:
You'll see Whiteside Salvaging
there, and Maxim-san should
be right next to it, mo.
